com.omerozer.knit.schedulers

Class ImmediateScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.omerozer.knit.schedulers.ImmediateScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SchedulerInterface

    public class ImmediateScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements SchedulerInterface
    This scheduler runs the tasks directly on the thread that it was fired from. Provides no async operations. The main use case is for Unit tests.
